### Phase 2 — MCQ Test System (13 new files)

#### Database Models
- [Test.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Test.ts) — title, duration, isActive, embedded questions
- [TestAttempt.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/TestAttempt.ts) — studentId, score, percentage, answers; unique index prevents re-taking

#### Parser Utility
- [mcqParser.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/lib/mcqParser.ts) — handles `Q1.`, `1.`, options `A)` / `A.` / [(A)](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/finance/fee-records/%5Bid%5D/route.ts#58-70), answers `Answer: B` / `Ans: B`, deduplicates, validates

#### Admin APIs (`/api/admin/tests/`)
- [GET](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/finance/fee-records/%5Bid%5D/route.ts#58-70) — list tests + attempt counts
- [POST](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/auth/send-otp/route.ts#21-87) — create test by parsing raw MCQ text
- `GET /[id]` — test detail + all student attempts
- `PATCH /[id]` — toggle isActive
- `DELETE /[id]` — remove test + all attempts

#### Student APIs (`/api/student/tests/`)
- [GET](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/api/admin/finance/fee-records/%5Bid%5D/route.ts#58-70) — active tests with "already attempted" flag (no answers exposed)
- `GET /[id]` — test questions (correct answers stripped)
- `POST /[id]` — submit, score server-side, return review with answer key

#### Admin Frontend
- [/admin/tests](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/admin/tests/page.tsx) — table with attempt counts, toggle, delete
- [/admin/tests/create](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/admin/tests/create/page.tsx) — paste MCQs textarea, example loader, parse result feedback

#### Student Frontend
- [/student/tests](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/%28student%29/student/tests/page.tsx) — test cards, score if attempted
- [/student/tests/\[id\]](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/%28student%29/student/tests/%5Bid%5D/page.tsx) — countdown timer, radio questions, auto-submit on timeout
- [/student/tests/\[id\]/result](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/%28student%29/student/tests/%5Bid%5D/result/page.tsx) — score card, grade, full review with correct/wrong colors

