### Phase 3 — Fee & Discount System (8 new files)

#### Model + Utilities
- [FeeRecord.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/FeeRecord.ts) — base price (locked), discount%, discountAmount, finalFees, payments[]
- [feeCalculator.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/lib/feeCalculator.ts) — [calcFees({ basePrice, discountPercent, flatDiscount })](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/lib/feeCalculator.ts#21-50) — guarded, centralised

#### Admin APIs
- `GET /api/admin/finance/fee-records` — list + revenue/dues totals, filterable
- `POST /api/admin/finance/fee-records` — create (validates discount ≤ base price)
- `PATCH /api/admin/finance/fee-records/[id]` — `action: "update-discount"` or `"add-payment"` (guards overpayment)

#### Student API
- `GET /api/student/fees` — returns only the logged-in student's own record

#### Frontend
- [/admin/finance/fees](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/admin/finance/fees/page.tsx) — summary cards, filterable table, Add Record modal with live discount calculator preview, Add Payment modal
- [/student/fees](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/%28student%29/student/fees/page.tsx) — fee summary card, payment progress bar, payment history list

