### Phase 4 — Google Analytics 4

Added to [layout.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/layout.tsx):
- GA4 `<Script>` tags (load strategy `afterInteractive`)
- Measurement ID via `NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID` env variable (defaults to placeholder `G-XXXXXXXXXX`)

> **Set up**: Add `NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_ID=G-YOUR_ACTUAL_ID` to your [.env](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/.env) file.

