## Test MCQ Parser

The parser handles all these formats correctly:

```
Q1. What is HTML?
A) Programming Language
B) Markup Language  ← selected as correct
C) Database
D) Server
Answer: B

1. CSS stands for?
A. Computer Style Sheets
B. Creative Style System
C. Cascading Style Sheets
D. Colorful Style Syntax
Ans: C
```

